---
import "../styles/base.css";

import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";

import heroBg from "@assetsLocal/renders/f32.png";
import flower from "@assetsLocal/icons/flower.svg";
import leafs from "@assetsLocal/icons/leafs.svg";
---

<MainLayout title="Revival">
	<section id="hero" class="w-full h-[60vh] xs:h-[75vh] s:h-[85vh] smd:h-[95vh] relative bg-[#DEDEDE] overflow-hidden">
		<img src={heroBg.src} alt="" class="absolute w-[220vw] s:w-[200vw] smd:w-[180vw] md:w-[160vw] m:w-[140vw] lg:w-[120vw] l:w-full bottom-0 -right-28 xs:-right-40 md:-right-20 m:-right-12 l:right-0 max-w-none">
		<div class="h-full flex m:items-stretch absolute left-[5%] lg:left-[7.5%] top-[15%] m:top-0">
			<div class="m:self-center flex flex-col w-3/4 md:w-1/2 l:w-1/3">
				<h2 class="uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">spoznajte</h2>
				<span class="title uppercase tracking-wider font-bold">Revival</span>
				<p class="text-secondary w-full sm:w-1/2 md:w-full l:w-full text-sm m:text-base mt-1">
					Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec tincidunt ullamcorper ex, nec bibendum metus sagittis vel.Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.
				</p>
				<a href="" class="primary-button mt-12 w-2/3 md:w-4/5 tracking-wider px-2 text-xs s:text-base hidden xs:block">Viac o Revivale</a>
			</div>
		</div>
		<a href="" class="primary-button mt-12 w-[70%] left-[15%] md:w-4/5 tracking-wider px-2 text-xs s:text-base block xs:hidden absolute bottom-4">Viac o Revivale</a>
	</section>

	<section id="about" class="content mt-24 flex flex-col">
		<h3 class="text-sm tracking-wider font-light text-center text-primary uppercase">o produkte</h3>
		<h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl tracking-wider font-black text-center mt-2 text-contrast uppercase">Čo je to revival</h1>

		<p class="text-tertiary w-full m:w-3/4 l:w-2/3 text-sm sm:text-base m:text-lg mt-4 sm:mt-8 text-center mx-auto tracking-wider">
			Fusce at tincidunt quam. Donec vitae ornare enim. Nullam dictum eu enim a porta. Morbi vitae dictum urna, sed pulvinar sapien. Praesent convallis ac nisi eu sodales. Nullam eleifend sodales ante. Vestibulum nec egestas nibh. Class aptent taciti sociosqu ad litora torquent per conubia nostra, per inceptos himenaeos. In hac habitasse platea dictumst. Donec nisl dui, dictum ultricies sem nec, lacinia imperdiet metus. Proin laoreet hendrerit arcu quis luctus.
		</p>

		<a href="" class="primary-button mx-auto mt-20 tracking-wider">Kúpiť Revival</a>

		<div class="mt-24 flex flex-col s:flex-row s:justify-around space-y-12 s:space-y-0 w-full md:w-3/4 lg:w-2/3 l:w-1/2 mx-auto">
			<div class="w-full s:w-1/3 mx-auto">
				<img src={flower.src} alt="" class="w-16 h-16 md:w-24 md:h-24 mx-auto">
				<h4 class="text-center mt-2 text-primary">Šetrný k prírode</h4>
			</div>
			<div class="w-full s:w-1/3 mx-auto">
				<img src={leafs.src} alt="" class="w-16 h-16 md:w-24 md:h-24 mx-auto">
				<h4 class="text-center mt-2 text-primary">Na prírodnej báze</h4>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</MainLayout>